    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> and your <strong>ground paprika</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until fragrant</p>",
